data.description: This charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom house sits gracefully on a sprawling 1-acre lot in the heart of Lebanon. As you enter, you'll be embraced by the warmth of a cozy fireplace in the inviting living room. The open concept design seamlessly connects the living room to the dining room and a beautifully appointed galley kitchen. Adjacent to the living room, a spacious bonus room awaits, offering versatility as a perfect family room. Heading upstairs, you'll find three well-appointed bedrooms and a conveniently located bathroom. This residence boasts notable upgrades, including a brand-new sewer system and recently installed windows on the main level. Conveniently located in proximity to shopping, dining, and more!
